Package dto

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AppointmentDTO
    A appointment DTO class lets transfer only the data that need to be share with the user interface on specific table/etc and not the entire model object.
    CustomerDTO
    A customer DTO class lets transfer only the data that need to be share with the user interface in specific table/etc and not the entire model object.
    CustomerReportDTO
    CustomerReportDTO transfers data from customer to the customer table in order to display data in specific format
    CustomerTableDTO
    CustomerTableDTO transfers data from customer to the customer table in order to display data in specific format
